<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>تسجيل الدخول | واتساب تكوين</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Tajawal:wght@400;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: 'Tajawal', sans-serif; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fdf4 0%, #f8fafc 100%); margin: 0; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-height: 100vh; padding: 20px; }
        .auth-card { background: white; padding: 40px; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); width: 100%; max-width: 420px; text-align: center; border-top: 4px solid #25d366; }
        .auth-card .logo { font-size: 40px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .auth-card h2 { margin-top: 0; color: #1e293b; font-weight: 800; font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 5px; }
        .auth-card p { color: #64748b; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 25px; }
        .input-group { margin-bottom: 18px; text-align: right; }
        .input-group label { display: block; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; color: #475569; margin-bottom: 6px; }
        .input-group input { width: 100%; padding: 12px 15px; border: 2px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 10px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s; }
        .input-group input:focus { border-color: #25d366; box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.1); }
        .btn { width: 100%; padding: 13px; background: #25d366; color: white; border: none; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; font-family: inherit; cursor: pointer; margin-top: 10px; transition: all 0.3s; }
        .btn:hover { background: #22c35e; transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.3); }
        .error { background: #fef2f2; color: #ef4444; padding: 12px; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: bold; border: 1px solid #fecaca; }
        .links { margin-top: 20px; font-size: 14px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
        .links a { color: #25d366; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; transition: 0.3s; }
        .links a:hover { color: #16a34a; }
        .back-link { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px; color: #94a3b8 !important; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 15px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="auth-card">
        <div class="logo">💬</div>
        <h2>مرحباً بعودتك!</h2>
        <p>سجّل دخولك للوصول إلى لوحة التحكم</p>
        <% if (error) { %><div class="error">⚠️ <%= error %></div><% } %>
        <form action="/login" method="POST">
            <div class="input-group">
                <label>اسم المستخدم</label>
                <input type="text" name="username" placeholder="أدخل اسم المستخدم" required autocomplete="username">
            </div>
            <div class="input-group">
                <label>كلمة المرور</label>
                <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="أدخل كلمة المرور" required autocomplete="current-password">
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn">تسجيل الدخول</button>
        </form>
        <div class="links">
            <a href="/forgot-password">نسيت كلمة المرور؟</a>
            <a href="/register">ليس لديك حساب؟ سجّل الآن</a>
            <a href="/" class="back-link">← العودة للصفحة الرئيسية</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
